    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being lost though. it's the stillness. everything is so quiet and empty at the edge. it feels like the only thing left to do is just stop fighting the wind and let the fog take me. like there's a certain kind of peace in finally just letting go of the path.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
